column19: YES   The car has only an upgraded exhaust. Other than that it is standard. It has not been rebuilt. It is very original. The value of this model the GTI G60 Edition One is its rarity. They rarely come onto the market. Many of the surging cars have been heavily modified and do not have the original engine. This one does. Please note the clock reading is in km and this car has less than 100 thousand miles on it which is very low and only has 2 previous U.K. owners.
